        <updateDate>2017-07-11T21:16:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ensuring the Reliability of Our Hurricane Hunter Aircraft Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration to maintain secondary backup capability for each class of hurricane reconnaissance, research, surveillance, and response aircraft sufficient to prevent a single point of failure. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
